                    <span>I agree with the reviewer who states that Will is not as hateful as the Clinton administration is. The Clinton administration destroyed computer keyboards and vandalized the White House and the Vice President's house to the point that both had to be completely razed and then rebuilt at the cost of approximately $25.6 billion dollars to the taxpayers. George Will, on the other hand, presents a factual and unbiased analysis of what is wrong with the fornicating, DNA splattering partial birth aborter and cigar-insertor who was our president.</span>
                  
              
